00:50:42.380 --> 00:50:44.860
Are you the real Qin?

00:50:45.340 --> 00:50:46.400
If he crosses the line,

00:50:46.440 --> 00:50:48.120
feel free to smack him.

00:50:48.860 --> 00:50:51.500
Why are you so adorable?

00:50:52.180 --> 00:50:53.700
Are you the real one?

00:50:54.580 --> 00:50:55.980
Are you?

00:51:11.880 --> 00:51:13.180
If it weren't for us,

00:51:13.370 --> 00:51:15.850
he'd have to wait until his next life
to stay over at Qin's place.

00:51:16.600 --> 00:51:17.600
Wait, Jamie.

00:51:18.280 --> 00:51:19.860
Duang's room
doesn't require a keycard.

00:51:21.820 --> 00:51:24.060
Come on, it was fine.

00:51:24.100 --> 00:51:25.220
It worked out, didn't it?

00:51:26.090 --> 00:51:28.020
- Let's go.
- How did you turn things around,

00:51:28.060 --> 00:51:28.980
- you genius?
- What?!

00:51:29.020 --> 00:51:29.900
Nothing.

00:51:48.260 --> 00:51:49.660
Hey...

00:52:10.140 --> 00:52:18.060
♫I used to be heartbroken
and drowned in tears♫

00:52:18.180 --> 00:52:23.600
♫So much so that
my heart told me to stop right there♫

00:52:23.840 --> 00:52:30.180
♫Then you came into my life,
changing this frozen heart♫

00:52:30.220 --> 00:52:36.100
♫It was once frozen solid,
but now it's starting to come alive♫

00:52:37.920 --> 00:52:41.300
♫The closer you are,
the more confused I become♫

00:52:41.340 --> 00:52:48.320
♫All I can do is ponder
the next step I should take♫

00:52:51.640 --> 00:53:01.780
♫You're not in the wrong,
all my heart can do is ask you these♫

00:53:02.680 --> 00:53:07.040
♫(If I love you...)
Tell me it won't make me bleed♫

00:53:07.080 --> 00:53:10.840
♫(If I love you...)
Will it end the same way it did?♫

00:53:10.880 --> 00:53:14.320
♫I don't understand myself either♫

00:53:14.360 --> 00:53:16.520
♫I'm worried I'd regret it,
like the past I had to suffer♫

00:53:16.560 --> 00:53:20.760
♫(If I don't love you...)
Will it be more heartbreaking?♫

00:53:20.800 --> 00:53:27.560
♫(Loving you) Might be better
than the painful past I had♫

00:53:27.600 --> 00:53:32.720
♫Should I say yes to this new love?♫

00:53:36.160 --> 00:53:37.760
You're looking at me?

00:53:39.880 --> 00:53:40.880
Mm.

00:53:43.000 --> 00:53:45.000
I'm thinking about what to do with you.

00:53:49.200 --> 00:53:50.800
Why are you mad at me?

00:53:51.800 --> 00:53:53.200
Can you please tell me?

00:53:57.560 --> 00:53:58.960
I won't do it again.

00:54:02.040 --> 00:54:03.240
Not now.

00:54:03.640 --> 00:54:05.160
I don't want to talk to a drunk person.

00:54:14.400 --> 00:54:15.600
I've sobered up.

00:54:24.440 --> 00:54:25.720
I'm actually not mad at you.

00:54:26.860 --> 00:54:28.220
You didn't do anything wrong.

00:54:31.920 --> 00:54:32.920
I simply...

00:54:35.000 --> 00:54:37.000
don't like it when I can't
control my emotions.

00:54:39.220 --> 00:54:41.020
I love it
when I've got nobody by my side.

00:54:41.440 --> 00:54:43.280
It's stable, safe,

00:54:44.560 --> 00:54:46.960
and there's not much to think about.

00:54:57.360 --> 00:54:58.800
It's because of me, isn't it?

00:54:59.280 --> 00:55:00.160
Yes.

00:55:03.860 --> 00:55:05.380
I won't do it again.

00:55:27.440 --> 00:55:28.920
You've done nothing,

00:55:29.400 --> 00:55:30.880
so why say that?

00:55:38.600 --> 00:55:39.760
What did you say?

00:55:43.800 --> 00:55:44.800
Nothing.

00:55:52.000 --> 00:55:53.000
I think...

00:55:54.300 --> 00:55:55.880
I'm going to take a shower.

00:55:57.200 --> 00:55:58.200
I'm having a headache.

00:56:04.600 --> 00:56:05.840
You don't say.

00:56:06.440 --> 00:56:07.720
You were recklessly drinking.

00:56:09.480 --> 00:56:10.600
So harsh.

00:56:11.720 --> 00:56:12.960
Go get a shower already,

00:56:14.320 --> 00:56:15.320
so you can go to bed.

00:56:23.100 --> 00:56:24.680
Even if you're harsh, I still love you.

00:56:29.960 --> 00:56:30.840
Get up.

00:56:53.960 --> 00:56:54.840
Hey!

00:57:10.560 --> 00:57:12.160
I'm not wearing any underwear.

00:57:14.520 --> 00:57:15.320
Ouch!

00:57:19.520 --> 00:57:21.320
Ow, that hurt!

00:57:21.960 --> 00:57:23.200
By the way...

00:57:23.240 --> 00:57:26.000
We both look like the characters
from 'Bananas in Pyjamas.'

00:57:26.200 --> 00:57:27.760
Hello, B1.

00:57:30.000 --> 00:57:31.600
You've sobered up, B2?

00:57:32.200 --> 00:57:33.400
Do you want to return to your place?

00:57:36.480 --> 00:57:38.200
I still can't walk straight.

00:57:53.020 --> 00:57:54.020
Qin.

00:58:05.520 --> 00:58:06.400
Huh?

00:58:09.840 --> 00:58:11.840
I'm not drunk, by the way.

00:58:15.600 --> 00:58:16.800
I like you.

00:58:19.120 --> 00:58:21.360
My feelings are
still the same as on the first day.

00:58:22.320 --> 00:58:24.520
I'm not here to pressure you.

00:58:25.280 --> 00:58:28.280
I just want you to know that
I haven't changed.

00:58:31.400 --> 00:58:34.600
I'm prepared to love you
with everything I have.

00:59:39.680 --> 00:59:41.280
Hey, you...

01:00:08.880 --> 01:00:10.040
Ow...

01:00:11.280 --> 01:00:13.040
That hurts!

01:00:14.530 --> 01:00:15.390
My bad.

01:00:15.600 --> 01:00:16.920
I...was caught off guard.

01:00:17.560 --> 01:00:19.160
You took a while.

01:00:19.200 --> 01:00:21.000
Those were some mad blows.

01:00:22.960 --> 01:00:24.520
It's fine, though. Since you're awake,

01:00:24.560 --> 01:00:26.640
I was thinking we could cuddle
and go back to sleep a bit more.

01:00:26.880 --> 01:00:27.640
Please?

01:00:29.040 --> 01:00:29.760
Hey!

01:00:36.920 --> 01:00:38.520
There's no dance practice
scheduled today.

01:00:38.560 --> 01:00:40.120
Since we're free, should we go out?

01:00:41.320 --> 01:00:44.480
Like, we can go on a date or something.

01:00:44.920 --> 01:00:45.800
Who says I am?

01:00:46.920 --> 01:00:48.400
I have plans to go out.

01:00:53.160 --> 01:00:54.320
Wanna come with?

01:00:55.360 --> 01:00:56.160
Yes, yes, yes!

01:00:56.200 --> 01:00:57.800
I wanna come with!

01:00:57.960 --> 01:00:58.960
Okay.

01:01:03.960 --> 01:01:05.200
You!

01:01:10.560 --> 01:01:13.280
Qin asked me out.

01:01:21.360 --> 01:01:22.280
Hey,

01:01:23.180 --> 01:01:24.180
wanna grab a bite first?

01:01:24.400 --> 01:01:25.800
No, we're gonna be late.

01:01:26.560 --> 01:01:27.560
For what?

01:01:27.960 --> 01:01:29.240
You're here to shop, aren't you?

01:01:29.280 --> 01:01:30.480
Or are you seeing someone?

01:01:31.740 --> 01:01:32.740
I'm not seeing anyone.

01:01:32.960 --> 01:01:33.920
You are.

01:01:38.840 --> 01:01:40.240
I'm down! It's just a tattoo.

01:01:40.280 --> 01:01:41.360
I'll pay you in advance, too.

01:01:41.400 --> 01:01:42.760
See you tomorrow at noon.

01:01:42.800 --> 01:01:43.760
There you go!

01:01:43.800 --> 01:01:45.480
Real man pays up!

01:01:47.120 --> 01:01:48.120
Holy shit.

01:01:48.940 --> 01:01:50.600
You knew about that?

01:01:50.640 --> 01:01:51.760
You screamed
for the whole bar to hear.

01:01:52.720 --> 01:01:54.120
Since you're such a show-off,
you need to show up.

01:01:55.240 --> 01:01:56.600
Jeez, you!

01:01:56.880 --> 01:01:58.640
I can just skip it.
It's not that much money, anyway.

01:01:59.920 --> 01:02:00.920
It's still money.

01:02:00.960 --> 01:02:02.120
Can I not go?

01:02:02.500 --> 01:02:03.760
I'm afraid of needles!

01:02:04.760 --> 01:02:05.600
Come on.

01:02:05.760 --> 01:02:06.680
Hey!

01:02:14.400 --> 01:02:15.840
How do you even know about this place?

01:02:22.240 --> 01:02:23.880
I confirmed two designs
for this appointment.

01:02:25.680 --> 01:02:26.600
So?

01:02:27.360 --> 01:02:28.800
I can just do one, right?

01:02:30.220 --> 01:02:32.220
It's such a shame
since the other one is so pretty.

01:02:41.200 --> 01:02:41.920
I'm just showing it to you,

01:02:41.960 --> 01:02:43.080
- not asking you to get one...
- I'll get one.

01:02:46.000 --> 01:02:47.720
I'm not forcing you or anything.

01:02:48.520 --> 01:02:49.800
You can't force me.

01:02:52.760 --> 01:02:54.320
Whoa!

01:02:54.480 --> 01:02:55.800
You're really here.

01:02:56.280 --> 01:02:58.000
Thought you'd chicken out
once you were sober.

01:02:58.040 --> 01:03:00.680
Jeez, bro. I already paid.

01:03:00.720 --> 01:03:02.120
- Don't want the money to go to waste?
- Mm.

01:03:02.480 --> 01:03:04.160
There are two of you.
Are you getting one each?

01:03:05.240 --> 01:03:06.480
Wow...

01:03:06.680 --> 01:03:08.760
You actually managed
to find someone else, huh?

01:03:09.040 --> 01:03:10.400
Alright, where do you want it tattooed?

01:03:10.720 --> 01:03:12.000
Inner ankle, please.

01:03:12.200 --> 01:03:13.200
What about you, Qin?

01:03:13.240 --> 01:03:14.720
Left ankle, please.

01:03:16.040 --> 01:03:18.240
Then I'm gonna do mine
on my right ankle.

01:03:22.440 --> 01:03:23.360
Okay, bet.

01:03:23.400 --> 01:03:25.120
Excuse me
while I prepare some equipment.

01:03:31.840 --> 01:03:32.840
Hey, you...

01:03:33.480 --> 01:03:34.360
Hey, hey, hey.

01:03:34.400 --> 01:03:36.040
I think I'll pass out for sure.

01:03:37.360 --> 01:03:38.360
It's not gonna hurt.

01:03:38.680 --> 01:03:39.640
Just as bad as a car crash.

01:03:39.680 --> 01:03:40.320
Huh?

01:03:40.800 --> 01:03:42.200
How does that not hurt?

01:03:42.560 --> 01:03:43.660
I read about it.

01:03:43.960 --> 01:03:44.960
Getting tattooed
on the ankles won't hurt.

01:03:45.600 --> 01:03:46.520
Really?

01:03:47.360 --> 01:03:48.230
Yeah.

01:03:48.400 --> 01:03:49.800
Did you do any research?

01:03:51.160 --> 01:03:52.160
I'm sorry...

01:03:55.080 --> 01:03:56.200
Do you want me to go first

01:03:56.240 --> 01:03:57.160
if you're gonna be this terrified?

01:03:57.200 --> 01:03:58.120
Not a chance.

01:03:58.360 --> 01:03:59.480
I wanna try it first.

01:03:59.520 --> 01:04:01.400
If it's too much,
you won't have to get it.

01:04:15.440 --> 01:04:16.720
Is it gonna hurt?

01:04:17.800 --> 01:04:19.200
Not too much.

01:04:19.680 --> 01:04:20.600
No sweat.

01:04:22.160 --> 01:04:23.060
Ready?

01:04:24.960 --> 01:04:25.960
I am.

01:04:26.560 --> 01:04:27.280
Okay.

01:04:28.080 --> 01:04:29.080
Here we go.

01:04:33.320 --> 01:04:33.800
I haven't started.

01:04:33.840 --> 01:04:34.520
Right.

01:04:36.080 --> 01:04:36.920
Three,

01:04:37.640 --> 01:04:38.400
two...

01:04:45.360 --> 01:04:46.280
Wanna hold it?

01:05:00.400 --> 01:05:01.600
Hold still.

01:05:02.760 --> 01:05:03.760
That hurts...

01:05:03.910 --> 01:05:05.240
No shit, you're getting a tattoo.

01:05:05.280 --> 01:05:06.400
Of course, it hurts.

01:05:07.400 --> 01:05:08.400
Here comes the color packing.

01:05:08.680 --> 01:05:09.680
It's gonna hurt a little.

01:05:10.600 --> 01:05:11.840
Is it gonna hurt a lot?

01:05:12.000 --> 01:05:13.440
Well, a little more than earlier.

01:05:13.680 --> 01:05:14.600
Like an ant bite?

01:05:14.640 --> 01:05:15.600
More like the whole colony.

01:05:24.440 --> 01:05:25.600
Almost done.

01:05:27.480 --> 01:05:30.360
Just a little more.

01:05:35.260 --> 01:05:35.980
Done.

01:05:36.480 --> 01:05:37.320
Ow...

01:05:40.040 --> 01:05:41.040
There you go.

01:05:46.360 --> 01:05:47.720
That's pretty.

01:05:47.760 --> 01:05:49.160
Here. Let me wipe it clean.

01:05:50.360 --> 01:05:51.600
The sun looks good on you.

01:05:58.880 --> 01:05:59.680
Come on.

01:06:00.080 --> 01:06:01.920
Let me put this wrap on it.

01:06:05.000 --> 01:06:07.600
And...don't get it wet

01:06:07.640 --> 01:06:09.400
for about a day.

01:06:09.520 --> 01:06:10.360
Okay.

01:06:10.520 --> 01:06:12.320
What do you say, Qin?
Ready for yours?

01:06:12.560 --> 01:06:13.360
Sure.

01:06:18.880 --> 01:06:20.080
Ow, I can feel it.

01:06:21.080 --> 01:06:22.720
Ouch, Smile, slow down!

01:06:23.080 --> 01:06:24.280
Ouch!

01:06:24.880 --> 01:06:26.320
Oww!

01:06:28.880 --> 01:06:30.080
Qin, does it hurt?

01:06:30.280 --> 01:06:31.160
No.

01:06:32.680 --> 01:06:34.280
How do you feel, Qin? Still good?

01:06:34.560 --> 01:06:35.480
I'm fine.

01:06:36.060 --> 01:06:37.400
See? He doesn't even feel it.

01:06:39.960 --> 01:06:40.960
No way.

01:06:41.000 --> 01:06:42.520
I'm sure he can feel it, too.

01:06:42.880 --> 01:06:44.920
- How do you know that?
- Ow, Smile! Be gentle!

01:06:44.960 --> 01:06:45.960
Ow!

01:06:46.160 --> 01:06:47.520
Just a little bit more
until the moon's done.

01:06:47.960 --> 01:06:50.360
Ow... Ouch!

01:06:51.880 --> 01:06:52.880
Excuse me, Qin.

01:06:53.240 --> 01:06:54.960
You get up.
Let him back on the bed.

01:06:56.320 --> 01:06:57.960
- What are you whining for?
- It just hurts

01:06:58.000 --> 01:06:59.840
- thinking he's in pain.
- Okay, then.

01:07:00.320 --> 01:07:01.320
You're worried, huh?

01:07:01.520 --> 01:07:02.520
Or is this your ankle?

01:07:03.120 --> 01:07:04.280
It's Qin's.

01:07:08.700 --> 01:07:09.700
Ow!

01:07:09.960 --> 01:07:11.360
Ow...

01:07:15.640 --> 01:07:17.760
Ow, did it hurt?

01:07:17.800 --> 01:07:18.520
Ooh...

01:07:18.880 --> 01:07:19.600
Oh...

01:07:19.980 --> 01:07:20.720
What?

01:07:21.560 --> 01:07:22.560
Why are you guys here?

01:07:25.280 --> 01:07:26.960
Oh...

01:07:27.000 --> 01:07:29.560
You are the ones who told Qin
where the shop is!

01:07:30.080 --> 01:07:31.080
What?

01:07:31.120 --> 01:07:33.520
You're nuts. I never told him
you were getting a tattoo here.

01:07:33.680 --> 01:07:35.560
- Was it you?
- Bro, what?

01:07:35.880 --> 01:07:37.120
Are you done getting tattooed?

01:07:37.900 --> 01:07:38.900
That's right, it is.

01:07:39.320 --> 01:07:40.680
Damn, that sucks.

01:07:40.960 --> 01:07:42.880
We came to watch you get tattooed.

01:07:43.320 --> 01:07:44.040
Did you get both designs?

01:07:44.080 --> 01:07:45.480
Both designs, my ass.

01:07:45.750 --> 01:07:47.070
Qin got one of them.

01:07:47.160 --> 01:07:49.000
Ooh!

01:07:49.680 --> 01:07:50.560
Noob.

01:07:51.040 --> 01:07:53.240
Don't get me started.

01:07:53.480 --> 01:07:55.320
It was like being slashed by a knife!

01:07:57.760 --> 01:07:59.040
Was it that bad, Qin?

01:07:59.160 --> 01:08:00.480
Or is he just being extra?

01:08:01.380 --> 01:08:02.360
It didn't hurt that bad.

01:08:02.400 --> 01:08:03.320
Yikes!

01:08:03.880 --> 01:08:05.280
What a noob.

01:08:06.680 --> 01:08:07.840
Hey, fam.

01:08:07.880 --> 01:08:09.120
- We have the whole squad here.
- Hi.

01:08:09.160 --> 01:08:10.320
Hi, there.

01:08:10.360 --> 01:08:11.360
Want a tattoo?

01:08:11.400 --> 01:08:12.400
I'll design one for you.

01:08:12.440 --> 01:08:13.720
I'll have to pass.

01:08:14.040 --> 01:08:15.040
My mom won't let me.

01:08:15.320 --> 01:08:16.399
What about you, Jamie?

01:08:16.880 --> 01:08:18.040
I'll have to think about it, bro.

01:08:18.080 --> 01:08:19.720
Tattooing needs
quite a lot of thinking, right?

01:08:19.760 --> 01:08:20.800
About the design and all.

01:08:20.840 --> 01:08:22.680
Keep up with the excuses.

01:08:22.720 --> 01:08:24.080
You're just a chicken, Jettana.

01:08:24.120 --> 01:08:25.319
You too, Prachai.

01:08:25.359 --> 01:08:26.520
What?

01:08:26.760 --> 01:08:28.840
I'm just loyal to my mom, unlike you,

01:08:28.880 --> 01:08:29.880
chicken.

01:08:30.479 --> 01:08:32.200
Yeah, at least I'm not you,

01:08:32.240 --> 01:08:33.080
a show-off boozer.

01:08:33.120 --> 01:08:34.200
In your face, sucker!

01:08:35.520 --> 01:08:36.399
How about this?

01:08:36.680 --> 01:08:37.680
If you can prove you're not chickens,

01:08:37.920 --> 01:08:38.680
I'll do it for free.

01:08:38.720 --> 01:08:39.359
Ooh...

01:08:39.520 --> 01:08:40.880
What a great deal...

01:08:41.319 --> 01:08:42.640
Whoa...

01:08:42.680 --> 01:08:43.359
Oh!

01:08:43.800 --> 01:08:45.359
Whoa... Mommy?

01:08:46.120 --> 01:08:46.920
Have you eaten?

01:08:46.960 --> 01:08:47.720
Wow!

01:08:49.000 --> 01:08:50.000
Papa!

01:08:50.520 --> 01:08:51.680
I miss you!

01:08:51.720 --> 01:08:53.960
Wow, what a bunch of chickens.

01:08:54.000 --> 01:08:55.160
Unlike me,

01:08:55.479 --> 01:08:57.080
who's as strong as a dog!

01:08:59.680 --> 01:09:00.680
A whiny one, sure.

01:09:01.960 --> 01:09:02.960
You were whining like a dog.

01:09:03.520 --> 01:09:04.920
- Thank you, Smile. Bye.
- Bye.

01:09:04.960 --> 01:09:05.880
Smile.

01:09:06.880 --> 01:09:07.760
See ya.

01:09:10.640 --> 01:09:11.960
Go home!

01:09:20.800 --> 01:09:22.800
Why are you taking
me back to your place?

01:09:23.180 --> 01:09:24.380
Are you having a mischievous plan?

01:09:26.040 --> 01:09:28.439
I have parents, you know?

01:09:31.240 --> 01:09:32.479
Go home, then.

01:09:32.640 --> 01:09:35.279
But my parents told me,

01:09:35.319 --> 01:09:36.800
"If you love someone,

01:09:36.840 --> 01:09:38.760
try spending the night
in their room first."

01:09:39.040 --> 01:09:40.600
I took you here
because it's already late.

01:09:41.060 --> 01:09:42.319
But if you wanna go back, be my guest.

01:09:42.819 --> 01:09:43.760
No way!

01:09:44.200 --> 01:09:45.399
I'm staying.

01:09:48.479 --> 01:09:49.479
Then I'll take a shower.

01:09:50.560 --> 01:09:51.840
Do you need a hand?

01:09:57.640 --> 01:09:58.520
Sure.

01:09:59.160 --> 01:09:59.840
Whoa...

01:10:00.120 --> 01:10:00.720
Hey...

01:10:01.440 --> 01:10:02.360
Whoa, whoa...

